{"tid":788864,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(文長)甚麼叫做玩fgo？","createTime":"2018-08-21T21:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T09:02:10.000Z","uid":7477,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"166ebe248957920f602ade93bc30f210f5882258","tid":788864,"uid":7477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T21:58:06.000Z","msg":"單機game中的滿足感<br />\n升LV 累積傷害 刷素材升技能<br />\n抽唔到既唔計 因為課金真係好貴同埋上癮性極高<br />\n自己抽到既servant假如有一項係可以未升好既都會有慾望去升好 <br />\n打個比喻就係好似好辛苦煮左餐飯然後全部跌曬落垃圾桶咁<br />\n升好之後(絆十) 就會將佢塞係倉庫唔用<br />\n<br />\n另一樣就係開放LV上限之後(140-150)<br />\n都好有意慾去升 但無奈我地係要上班工作一日之中有好多其他野要運作<br />\n所以都係好絕望<br />\n<br />\n結論：山翁pick up既時候我希望最少都可以寶2到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/054223_a0b2607f392a9e148677358b279ee3c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F054223_a0b2607f392a9e148677358b279ee3c6.png&h=93772f63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1b7971d2e4bfc7f1a1c672a9fafc5bf51b0c39a","tid":788864,"uid":168161,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T22:18:06.000Z","msg":"2018仲玩fgo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇考慮過轉玩gbf?"},{"pid":"628c9b0bfe457ac911e04af84b3e5337295ec405","tid":788864,"uid":2794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T22:38:52.000Z","msg":"動物台大阿哥回來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可喜可賀"},{"pid":"6fdc40234cc3bdf54eb85b4849b8462592ce71a5","tid":788864,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T23:45:42.000Z","msg":"叉叉助手"},{"pid":"b2c9956d9dda6fc260e6c53f3eb7411d41d3d46d","tid":788864,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:10:59.000Z","msg":"你個ac比人封幾耐"},{"pid":"fe5ffa275dd699090abd4cf2bf1b7d31015d0b5f","tid":788864,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"🏧"},{"pid":"3fb6b3d662c5cbae516